reviewText: This DVD contains Milton Nascimento's musical Life from the beginnings to now. You can listen to various pieces and styles by himself. Travessia is generally Milton Nascimeno's jouney in his Musical Life, where he is combinating various styles in one style. Many People are calling this Style "Milton e Minas". "Milton" - the Name of this famous Composer and Interpreter, and "Minas" the place "Minas Gerais" where he was spending his childhood and was developping his genial Music
